                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I'll tell you how the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Sun rose - </l>
                    <l>A Ribbon at a time - </l>
                    <l>The Steeples swam in<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Amethyst - </l>
                    <l>The news, like Squirrels,<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 ran - </l>
                    <l>The Hills untied their<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Bonnets -</l>
                    <l>The Bobolinks - begun - </l>
                    <l>Then I said softly to<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 myself - </l>
                    <l>&quot;That must have been<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 the Sun&quot;!  </l>
                    <l>But how he set -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 I know not - </l>
                    <l>There seemed a purple<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 stile</l>
                    <l>That little Yellow boys<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 and girls </l>
                    <l>Were climbing all the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 while - </l>
                    <l>Till when they reached<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 the other side - </l>
                    <l>A Dominie in Gray - </l>
                    <l>Put gently up the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 evening Bars -</l>
                    <l>And led the flock<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 away - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
